Homeownership Rate in USA

Omkar Pawar

Import Data from Census Homeownership Rate according to race.

Now we have data loaded. From the column names we can see that the first column has the race and remaining columns are per year home ownership rates.

rr df1<-as.data.frame(t(new_df))

US Homeownership Rate and Minorities Homeownership Rate

Homeownership Rate Comparision between Whites and Black population

rr ggplot(data = df1 , aes(x = Year , group = 1) ) + geom_line(aes(y = Overall_US , colour = _US)) +

geom_line(aes(y = Non_Hispanic_Whites , colour = _Hispanic_Whites))+ geom_line(aes(y = African_American , colour = _American))+

geom_line(aes(y = American.Indian.or.Alaskan.Native.alone , colour = .Indian.or.Alaskan.Native.alone))+ geom_line(aes(y = Asian.or.Native.Hawaiian.Pacific.Islander.alone , colour = .or.Native.Hawaiian.Pacific.Islander.alone))+ geom_line(aes(y = Hispanic.or.Latino , colour = .or.Latino))+

scale_colour_manual(\, breaks = c(_US, _Hispanic_Whites, _American,.Indian.or.Alaskan.Native.alone,.or.Native.Hawaiian.Pacific.Islander.alone,.or.Latino), values = c(#999999, #56B4E9, , #0072B2, #D55E00, #CC79A7))+ scale_y_continuous(Rate, limits = c(40,80))+ theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1))

All Possible Race and Ethnicity Values

rr ggplot(data = df1 , aes(x = Year , group = 1) ) + geom_line(aes(y = Overall_US , colour = _US)) + geom_line(aes(y = All_Whites , colour = _Whites))+ geom_line(aes(y = Non_Hispanic_Whites , colour = _Hispanic_Whites))+ geom_line(aes(y = African_American , colour = _American))+ geom_line(aes(y = Minorities , colour = ))+ geom_line(aes(y = American.Indian.or.Alaskan.Native.alone , colour = .Indian.or.Alaskan.Native.alone))+ geom_line(aes(y = Asian.or.Native.Hawaiian.Pacific.Islander.alone , colour = .or.Native.Hawaiian.Pacific.Islander.alone))+ geom_line(aes(y = Hispanic.or.Latino , colour = .or.Latino))+ geom_line(aes(y = Non.Hispanic , colour = .Hispanic))+ scale_colour_manual(\, breaks = c(_US, _Whites,_Hispanic_Whites, _American,,.Indian.or.Alaskan.Native.alone,.or.Native.Hawaiian.Pacific.Islander.alone,.or.Latino,.Hispanic), values = c(#999999, #E69F00, #56B4E9, #009E73, , #0072B2, #D55E00, #CC79A7,#293352))+ scale_y_continuous(Rate, limits = c(40,80)) + theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1))+ labs(title = Possible Race and Ethnicity Values)
